simplepicture (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Support PNG, JPG, BMP, GIF, WEBP, TIFF, ICO, SVG formats.
  * Mouse wheel zoom and keyboard navigation.
  * SVG vector rendering with lossless zoom.

